-- MOVES-Cordea Savills names Jin Guo as head of Greater China
-- 
-- Mon Oct 13, 2014 06:27AM EDT
-- None



Oct 13 (Reuters) - Property investment manager Cordea Savills named Jin Guo as head of Greater China, to lead new business initiatives with institutions, family offices and private wealth managers.

Jin joins from ICBC International Investment Management Ltd, where he played a leading role in establishing real estate funds in Mainland China for state-owned entities as well as providing strategic advice on fund governance.